Scrambled eggs 

Ingredients:
4x Eggs
1 teaspoon salt
1 teaspoon pepper
1 tablespoon of milk
Shredded cheese
1 teaspoon of cooking oil or butter
1 quarter cup of spinach

Steps:
(0) First of all, don't forget to wash the spinach!
(1) Grease cooking pan and set flame to low
(2) Combine eggs into bowl and whisk until scrambled, be sure not to over mix
(3) Add milk, spinach and spices, mix gentley until combined
(4) Continuously stir until liquid egg has formed a solid scramble
(5) Remove from heat, plate and enjoy!
